				\begin{document}$$min = \mathop \sum \limits_{\lambda = 1}^{n} \left( {R_{\lambda } - \widetilde{{R_{\lambda } }}} \right)^{2}$$\end{document}min=∑λ=1nRλ-Rλ~2where Rλ and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
